Class InternalAuthority

  • java.lang.Object
    • workshop.internal.entities.WorkshopEntityAbstract
      • workshop.internal.entities.Trackable
        • workshop.internal.entities.InternalAuthority
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WorkshopEntity>, org.springframework.security.core.GrantedAuthority, WorkshopEntity

    @Entity(name="Internal_Authority")
public class InternalAuthority
extends Trackable
implements org.springframework.security.core.GrantedAuthority
    Serves as the GrantedAuthority for the INTERNAL.Employees for fine tuning their PermissionType. The class is the container for PermissionType.
